	* share/mpi/mpil_spawn.c (spawn): clear RTF_FLAT.

	* share/trillium/rload.c (rload): initialize bmalloc to FALSE.



5.2
---

DATE	AUTHOR	STATUS	DESCRIPTION

8/22		rel	LAM 5.2

