			(otb/mpirun/mpirun.c)

9/2	JRV	fix	Don't modify pointers you intend to use later.
			(otb/mpirun/mpirun.c)

9/8	RBD	fix	Change _kio_cleanup() to _cio_cleanup() in pvm_exit().
			(share/pvm/exit.c)

